params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The resource in which to create the log bucket: "projects/[PROJECT_ID]/locations/[LOCATION_ID]" For example: "projects/my-project/locations/global"

params.name: data.bucket_id
params.description: Required. A client-assigned identifier such as "my-bucket". Identifiers are limited to 100 characters and can include only letters, digits, underscores, hyphens, and periods.

params.name: data.bucket
params.description: Required. The new bucket. The region specified in the new bucket must be compliant with any Location Restriction Org Policy. The name field in the bucket is ignored.
